      "value": "<p>&gt;<span>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.sFIvlvRtBJ0EH2Jt]{First World}</span></p>\n<p>As a standard action, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to open a portal to the First World within 100 feet. Mischievous fey swarm through this portal, attacking all enemies in a 20-foot-radius spread. Each enemy in the area is the target of one of the following combat maneuvers: dirty trick, disarm, or trip. You select the action individually for each enemy targeted. The attack roll for these actions is equal to your caster level plus your Wisdom modifier. Their mischief concluded, the fey immediately return to the First World, and the portal closes.</p>"
